<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema516_15_su_0003" data-current-page="page_1, page_2, page_3, page_4, page_5">
    <section class="title type2 page-1-title">
      <h2 lang="y" data-head="2">
        주환이네 마을에 둘레가 1600 m이면서 넓이가 가장 넓은 직사각형 모양의 공원을 만들려고 합니다. 만들 수 있는 가장 넓은 공원의 넓이는 몇 ㎡인지 구해 봅시다. (단, 변의 길이는 100 m씩
        늘이거나 줄일 수 있습니다.)
      </h2>
    </section>
    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <article class="page page_1">
        <h3 lang="y">둘레가 1600 m인 직사각형의 가로와 세로의 합은 몇 m인가요?</h3>
        <div class="flex align_center gap_12 flex_wrap">
          <div class="input_wrap answer1">
            <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="1400" text-align="center"></math-field>
            <span>m</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article><!-- 4page -->

      <article class="page page_2">
        <section class="title type2"></section>
        <h3 lang="y">
          둘레가 1600 m인 서로 다른 직사각형을 3가지 그려 보세요.
        </h3>
        <div class="input_area">
          <div class="question_box dir_col align_start">
            <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
              <div class="img_area">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_15_SU/15_03_bg2.png" alt="배경 이미지" />
                <div class="length1">
                  <span>100 m</span>
                </div>
                <div class="length2">
                  <span>100 m</span>
                </div>
                <div class="length3">
                  <span>10000 ㎠</span>
                </div>
                <div class="canvas-wrap">
                  <div id="square">
                    </di>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_15_SU/15_03_ex2.svg" alt="정답 이미지">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- 2page -->
      <article class="page page_3">
        <h3 lang="y">
          내가 그린 직사각형과 친구가 그린 직사각형의 넓이를 비교해 보세요.
        </h3>
        <div class="input_area">
          <div class="input_wrap">
            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
            <div class="example_box">
              <p lang="y">내가 그린 직사각형의 넓이는 각각 70000 ㎡, 150000 ㎡, 160000 ㎡이고, 친구가 그린 직사각형의 넓이는<br />각각 120000 ㎡,
                150000 ㎡, 70000 ㎡ 입니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </article>
      <!-- 3page -->
      <article class="page page_4">
        <h3 lang="y">
          표를 완성하여 둘레가 1600 m인 직사각형의 넓이를 모두 구해 보세요.
        </h3>
        <div class="input_area">
          <table>
            <tr>
              <th class="top_table">가로 (m)</th>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field text-type="number" data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="200"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="300"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="400"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="500"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="600"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td class="right_table">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="700"></math-field>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>세로 (m)</th>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="700"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="600"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="500"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="400"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="300"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="200"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th class="bottom_table">둘레 (m)</th>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="70000"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="120000"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="150000"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="160000"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="150000"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td class="end_table">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="120000"></math-field>
              </td>
              <td>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="70000"></math-field>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- 4page -->
      <article class="page page_5">
        <h3 lang="y">만들 수 있는 가장 넓은 공원의 넓이는 몇 ㎡인가요?</h3>
        <div class="flex align_center gap_12 flex_wrap">
          <div class="input_wrap answer1">
            <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="160000" text-align="center"></math-field>
            <span>㎡</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article><!-- 5page -->
      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
